  <title>Safe &amp; Secure - promoting children&#x2019;s rights to care and protection</title>
  <description>The aim of this project is to ensure a safe environment for the most vulnerable children, including children with disabilities, in the target communities.  This will be achieved by strengthening the national and community-based child protection mechanisms in the target communities and by empowering the children of the targeted areas in addressing child protection concerns to the relevant mechanisms.</description>
